About The Project

Extracta allows us to catalog data and query by the content of the file instead of its name. Utilizing AI, Extracta generates and appends tags based on the incoming file type.

Uploading audio generates a transcription, appending key words and sentiment.
Uploading images generates labels, appending whats actually inside of the image directly to the file.
Uploading pdfs appends key words and sentiment.

Stop trying to remember what file name has what data, use Extracta, and query based on what you need.
